statements.sql: select `p`.`productosid`, `p`.`productocodigo`, `p`.`descripcion`, `pt`.`precioiva` as `precio2`, `pi`.`imagen`, `p`.`parametros_json`, `ventas`.`total_cantidad`, (SELECT tarifain.precioiva FROM productos_tarifas as tarifain WHERE tarifain.tarifasid = 1 and tarifain.productosid = p.productosid AND tarifain.medidasid = p.unidadinterna) AS precio from `productos` as `p` inner join `productos_tarifas` as `pt` on `pt`.`productosid` = `p`.`productosid` left join `productos_imagenes` as `pi` on `pi`.`productosid` = `p`.`productosid` and `pi`.`principal` = 1 inner join (select `fd`.`productosid`, SUM(CASE WHEN (f.sri_documentoscodigo = '04') THEN (fd.cantidad * -1) ELSE fd.cantidad END) AS total_cantidad from `facturas_detalles` as `fd` inner join `facturas` as `f` on `fd`.`facturasid` = `f`.`facturasid` where `f`.`emision` >= '2023-10-31 11:26:00' group by `fd`.`productosid` order by `total_cantidad` desc limit 10) as `ventas` on `ventas`.`productosid` = `p`.`productosid` where `p`.`ecommerce_estado` in (1, 2) and `p`.`existenciastotales` > 0 and `pt`.`tarifasid` = 1 and `p`.`venta` = 1 and `p`.`servicio` = 0 and `p`.`bien` = 0 and `pt`.`medidasid` = `p`.`unidadinterna` order by `ventas`.`total_cantidad` desc limit 10
